    <h1>About Movie Review & Search App</h1>

    <p>Welcome to the Movie Review & Search App! Our platform allows you to search for your favorite movies, explore detailed information about them, and share your opinions with other movie enthusiasts.</p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Search Movies:</strong> Enter a movie title to search through a vast collection of movies from various genres, time periods, and countries.</li>
      <li><strong>Movie Details:</strong> Click on any movie to view its full details, including its plot summary, cast, and ratings.</li>
      <li><strong>Movie Reviews:</strong> Coming soon: Share your reviews and read what others have to say about a movie.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Powered by TMDb API</h2>
    <p>This app is powered by the <a href="https://www.themoviedb.org/" target="_blank">The Movie Database (TMDb) API</a>, providing reliable and up-to-date information about thousands of movies across the globe.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Our goal is to provide a simple, intuitive platform where movie fans can find information on the latest films, discover hidden gems, and share their movie-watching experiences with a community of fellow enthusiasts.</p>

    <p>Feel free to explore the app and let us know if you have any feedback or suggestions!</p>
